    "rel": "noreferrer"
  }), "OPNSense"), ". These distributions have minimal support for ARM-based boards, and finding x86 hardware with low power consumption, reasonable price, and decent performance is not that easy."), mdx("p", null, "Then I remembered on my ", mdx("a", _extends({
